活动，您将为红十字国际委员会的重要工作提供支持。">为红十字国际委员会筹款</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/bequests-and-legacies" title="">遗赠和遗产</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/friends-icrc" title="">红十字国际委员会之友</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/foundations" title="">与基金会或信托机构合作</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/philanthropy" title="">进行大额捐款</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/corporate-support" title="">与公司合作</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/support-us/audience/planned-giving" title="">有计划捐助</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container pull-right hidden-xs hidden-sm"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/donate" class="bg-red nav-link-main">捐款</a></div></div></div></div> </nav></div><div class="region region-content"><div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system"><div class="content"> <section class="clearfix breadcrumb-wrapper theme-brown"><div class="container"><ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="i-arrow-right-after"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh">主页</a></li><li class="i-arrow-right-after"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law">战争与法律</a></li><li class="i-arrow-right-after"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl">当前国际人道法热点问题</a></li><li class="active js_toggle i-arrow-up" data-target=".breadcrumb-wrapper">恐怖主义</li></ol></div></section><section class="section-hero theme-brown"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-12"><h1 class="h1 font-xs-40 font-md-60">恐怖主义</h1><div class="topic-body font-xs-16 font-md-18"><p>大部分在和平时期被称为“恐怖主义”的行为在战争中也是为国际人道法所禁止的。在这种背景下，国际人道法既适用于正规武装部队，也适用于非国家武装团体。发生在其他局势下的恐怖主义行为会受到其他法律体系的约束，特别是国内刑法的制约。<br /><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/challenges-ihl-terrorism-overview">查阅更多内容</a></p></div></div></div></div> </section><section class="theme-brown vspace-top-small visible-xs visible-sm container"><div class="navbar navbar--switch"> <nav class="clearfix font-xs-12 js_toggle" data-target=".switch_container" data-settings='{"behaviour":"switch", "clickoutside":false}' role="navigation"> <a href="#" class="active col-xs-6" data-state="inactive">新闻</a> <a href="#" class="col-xs-6" data-state="active">详情</a> </nav></div></section><section class="vspace-bottom vspace-top-small container"><div class="clearfix switch_mask row"><div class="switch_container"> <main class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-8"><div class="theme-brown"><div class="row vspace-bottom-small"><div class="col-md-12 text-center"><div class="social-icons social-icons--theme clearfix font-xs-12 font-md-18"> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-sina-weibo i-sina-weibo-color" href="http://service.weibo.com/share/share.php?url=https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism" target="_blank" title="分享至新浪微博"> <span class="sr-only">分享至新浪微博</span> </a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-douban i-douban-color" href="https://www.douban.com/share/service?href=https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism" target="_blank" title="分享至豆瓣"> <span class="sr-only">分享至豆瓣</span> </a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-tieba i-tieba-color" href="http://tieba.baidu.com/f/commit/share/openShareApi?url=https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism" target="_blank" title="分享至贴吧"> <span class="sr-only">分享至贴吧</span> </a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-qzone i-qzone-color" href="http://sns.qzone.qq.com/cgi-bin/qzshare/cgi_qzshare_onekey?url=https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism" target="_blank" title="分享至QQ空间"> <span class="sr-only">分享至QQ空间</span> </a></div></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-12"><div class="navbar navbar--switch"> <nav class="clearfix font-xs-12 js_toggle-document-list" data-target=".switch_container-document-list" data-settings='{"behaviour":"switch", "clickoutside":false}' role="navigation"> <a href="#" class="col-xs-6 active" data-state="inactive">最近资讯</a> <a href="#" class="col-xs-6" data-state="active">推荐热文</a> </nav></div></div></div><div class="row document-list switch_mask"><div class="switch_container-document-list"><div id="document-list" class="col-sm-12"><ul class="list-related "><li><div class="heading-meta clearfix font-sm-12"> 2019-11-22 <span class="seperator-left">报告</span></div> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/icrc-report-ihl-and-challenges-contemporary-armed-conflicts">红十字国际委员会关于“国际人道法及其在当代武装冲突中面临的挑战”报告</a></li><li><div class="heading-meta clearfix font-sm-12"> 2019-09-26 <span class="seperator-left">发言</span></div> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/combatting-terrorism-should-not-come-expense-humanitarian-action-or-principles">反恐不应以人道行动或人道原则为代价</a></li><li><div class="heading-meta clearfix font-sm-12"> 2017-07-19 <span class="seperator-left">报道</span></div> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/guidance-note-national-societies-preventing-and-countering-violent-extremism-approach">“预防与打击暴力极端主义”举措：针对国家红会的指导性说明</a></li><li><div class="heading-meta clearfix font-sm-12"> 2017-05-17 <span class="seperator-left">视频</span></div> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/china-helen-durham-interview-ihl">红十字国际委员会国际法与政策部主任海伦·德拉姆博士访谈</a></li><li><div class="heading-meta clearfix font-sm-12"> 2015-10-31 <span class="seperator-left">报告</span></div> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/international-humanitarian-law-and-challenges-contemporary-armed-conflicts">国际人道法及其在当代武装冲突中面临的挑战</a></li><li><div class="heading-meta clearfix font-sm-12"> 2015-01-22 <span class="seperator-left">报道</span></div> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/what-does-ihl-say-about-terrorism">国际人道法对恐怖主义有什么规定？</a></li><li><div class="heading-meta clearfix font-sm-12"> 2010-10-29 <span class="seperator-left">报道</span></div> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/zh/document/challenges-ihl-terrorism-overview">国际人道法面临的挑